high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the stove.
Pick up the cast iron pan on the back burner.
Turn left to go to the front of the refrigerator on the right.
Chill the pan in the refrigerator on the bottom shelf below the apple and take it out and close the refrigerator door.
Turn right and move over to the counter on the left of the stove.
Place the pan on the counter top on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the white stove on the left.
Pick up the black pan from the back right corner of the stove.
Turn left and walk to the black fridge on your right.
Put the pan inside the fridge on the left side of the bottom shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the doors.
Turn right and walk to the counter next to the fridge on the left side.
Put the chilled pan on the left side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and find the stove on the left.
Pick up the pot from the back right burner.
Carry the pot and move to the left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot inside. Shut the fridge the open it and take the pot out. Shut the door.
Carry the pot and move a few steps right.
Place the pot on the counter, to the right of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and place it on the counter.
